que he abierto las puertas." Sigue, Pavón.

16
00:03:10,691 --> 00:03:12,364
<i>And opened up the doors.</i>

17
00:03:13,610 --> 00:03:15,908
<i>Help me if you can, I'm feeling down.</i>

18
00:03:15,987 --> 00:03:18,456
