19
00:03:18,573 --> 00:03:21,167
<i>And I do appreciate you being around.</i>

20
00:03:21,243 --> 00:03:24,087
Y me encantaría tenerte cerca.

21
00:03:24,413 --> 00:03:26,757
<i>Help me get my feet back on the ground.</i>

22
